description: This skill retrieves air quality report containing current levels for Ozone, Small Particles (if reported) and Large Particles (if reported) for any US 5-digit ZIP code, using date provided by the US Environmental Protection Agency (EPA).
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask air quality report for zip code nine eight one zero nine
Alexa, ask air quality report in zip code nine eight one zero nine
Alexa, ask air quality report at zip code nine eight one zero nine
name: Air Quality Report
shortDescription: Get air quality report for 5-digit US ZIP codes
